# MAKE IBG MELEE ONLY

Its probably a little bit off topic, but what about updating the item icons/art? New and reworked items have already up-to-date art, but for a game that is continually updating I feel like most of the item icons are in a need for an update. League of Legends is a game that looks modern and fresh, but most items dont even look like they are part of this game. Some even look very crappy, like they are made in paint.

It's just something small I've always wondered about why it's not updated.
